title: Bobby's Beef With New Duo 'Seaforth' + Tim Tebow Talks About Prank Wars With Luke Bryan + Bobby Helps A Listener With Marital Struggles
itunes:title: Bobby's Beef With New Duo 'Seaforth' + Tim Tebow Talks About Prank Wars With Luke Bryan + Bobby Helps A Listener With Marital Struggles
description:
Bobby talks to the duo 'Seaforth' about the accusation Eddie made about them stealing their Raging Idiots' look. He challenges them to a competition for the rights to the look! A listener has an interesting situation going on with his wife. He claims she doesn’t want to do anything around the house, but we think there’s much more to it. Plus, Bobby talks to Tim Tebow about his prank war with Luke Bryan, his new kid’s book and how he prepared for big games!
